INSERT INTO `events` VALUES (2,3,NULL,'Studentfoire Luxembourg','2016-11-09 00:00:00','2016-11-10 00:00:00','','http://openagenda.com/event/studentfoire-luxembourg','Venez sur le stand EPITECH à la rencontre de nos étudiants !','','http://cibul.s3.amazonaws.com/event_studentfoire-luxembourg_13821.jpg',NULL),(3,3,NULL,'Sore; Pissos; Luxey','2017-03-04 00:00:00','2017-03-04 00:00:00','','http://openagenda.com/event/sore-pissos-luxey','','','',NULL),(4,3,NULL,'Fête de la Quetsche Larochette','2016-10-09 00:00:00','2016-10-09 00:00:00','','http://openagenda.com/event/fete-de-la-quetsche-larochette','','','http://cibul.s3.amazonaws.com/event_fete-de-la-quetsche-larochette_669534.jpg',NULL),(5,3,NULL,'Luxure','2013-10-05 00:00:00','2013-10-05 00:00:00','','http://openagenda.com/event/luxure','Pour sa septième édition, le WunderKabarett va vous faire entrer dans le monde du stupre, de la débauche et du dévergondage!!!\nVenez découvrir les Cocotes, demi-mondaines, hétaïres, call-girls, créatures, belles de nuit, les poules de luxe et les filles de mauvaise vie... !!!\nVous rencontrerez La belle Otero, La Marquise de Pompadour, Mata Hari, Irma la Douce, Zahia, Madame Claude, les joyaux du harem de Topkapi ...','cabaret,burlesque,cantada,effeuilleuses,effeuillage','http://cibul.s3.amazonaws.com/event_luxure_788239.jpg',NULL),(6,3,NULL,'Visite commentée','2016-09-17 00:00:00','2016-09-17 00:00:00','','http://openagenda.com/event/conference_870','Durée 1h.','','',NULL),(7,3,NULL,'GR Business Days 2014','2014-06-18 00:00:00','2014-06-19 00:00:00','','http://openagenda.com/event/gr-business-days-2014','Site de l\'événement: www.gr-businessdays.com\nProgramme: http://bit.ly/1mMRmOM\nÉvénements-clés: http://bit.ly/1nKSo33\n\nGR Business Days: Une vue à 360° sur les opportunités d\'affaires prometteuses au sein de la Grande Région et au-delà!\n\n- Proposer une ambiance riche et efficace pour l’établissement de relations professionnelles amplifiant les effets de divers outils d’expansion de marché;\n- Combiner les techniques traditionnelles d’internationalisation avec des outils marketing de nouvelle génération à caractère international;\n- Présenter les entreprises avec un accès facilité à des chefs d’entreprise et décideurs clés;\n\nSecteurs cibles: \nTIC, e-commerce, biotechnologie, matériaux, développement durable, banque et finance...\n\nLes Greater Region Business Days proposeront plusieurs micro-événements sur deux jours employant différents aspects du networking sur place et l’établissement de partenariats. Le but de l’organisateur est de construire une plate-forme dynamique répondant aux demandes de PMEs dans le contraignant scénario économique actuel en fournissant de nouvelles opportunités d’affaires.\n\nA travers les GR Business Days, vous disposerez de plus de moyens intéressants pour trouver de nouveaux partenaires, élargir la gamme de vos produits et services, explorer de nouvelles technologies et plus encore… En outre, vous aurez la possibilité de participer aux conférences interactives, ateliers, réceptions de networking, et au symposium afin d’avoir un aperçu des perspectives économiques de la communauté professionnelle dans la Grande Région et au-delà.','innovation,grande région,luxembourg,startups,ecommerce,TIC,matériaux,networking,pitchs,sillon lorrain','http://cibul.s3.amazonaws.com/event_gr-business-days-2014_897825.jpg',NULL),(8,3,NULL,'Journée du Patrimoine au château de Lux','2015-09-20 00:00:00','2015-09-20 00:00:00','','http://openagenda.com/event/journe-du-patrimoine-au-chteau-de-lux','','21,21000','http://cibul.s3.amazonaws.com/event84356482.jpg',NULL),(9,3,NULL,'Séminaire La Royale','2016-05-05 00:00:00','2016-05-05 00:00:00','','http://openagenda.com/event/seminaire-la-royale_5','Amyris sera également présent à trois séminaires de La-Royale durant le mois de mai : le jeudi 05 mai à Pétange (Luxembourg) où le thème du séminaire sera  \"Pratiques de thérapeutes. Maladies de civilisations\"  avec les Docteurs Bruno Chacornac, Patrick Depoërs et Franck Ledoux comme formateurs.','','http://cibul.s3.amazonaws.com/event_seminaire-la-royale_5_751876.jpg',NULL),(10,3,NULL,'Fête de la Musique au Luxembourg','2015-06-21 00:00:00','2015-06-21 00:00:00','','http://openagenda.com/event/fete-de-la-musique-au-luxembourg','http://www.fetedelamusique.lu/\n\nLe programme 2015 :\nhttp://www.fetedelamusique.lu/Programme-2015/20150621','Luxemburg','http://cibul.s3.amazonaws.com/event_fete-de-la-musique-au-luxembourg_678793.jpg',NULL),(11,3,NULL,'Visite du château de Lux','2016-09-18 00:00:00','2016-09-18 00:00:00','','http://openagenda.com/event/visite-du-chateau-de-lux','Visites guidées uniquement, visite libre du parc.\n\nVisite entre 45 minutes et une heure.','','',NULL),(12,2,NULL,'','2017-03-12 09:00:00','2017-03-12 12:00:00','','https://www.meetup.com/Yoga-in-Luxembourg/events/236601956/','<p><b>Detox Program to start your New Year with Health and Wellness</b></p> <p>This is a series of 6 workshops with 90 minutes of Yin yoga and 90 minutes of Yang yoga taught by two certified yoga teachers, Axinja Granier and Kelsey Hopper.</p> <p><b>Times</b></p> <p>9h00  - 10h30 Yin Yoga (very soft and slow) <br/>10h30 - 12h00 Yang Yoga (more dynamic, vinyasa flow)</p> <p>12h00 - reception with healthy, vegan food &amp; drink</p> <p><b>Price all Six Workshops: </b>210€ <br/><b>Price One Workshop: </b>50€ drop in, 40€ early bird (payment <b><i>received</i></b> 2 weeks before class)</p> <p><br/><b>Themes</b></p> <p>- Back from Holidays De-Stress &amp; Detox (January 15)</p> <p>- Weight Loss Detox (January 29)</p> <p>- Digestive System Detox (12 February)</p> <p>- Immune System Boost (5 March)</p> <p>- Thyroid Balance and Metabolism Boost (12 March)</p> <p>- Spring Cleaning Detox (26 March</p> <p><b>9h00-10h30 Yin Yoga </b></p> <p>Soft and slow, most poses are done on the floor.  Gravity and time (poses are held 3-5 minutes) help to release deeper into the pose and apply healthy stress to connective tissues, making them stronger, more flexible and increasing circulation in the joints.   Yin Yoga balances the meridians (energy channels), releases chronic and long held tensions, as well as negative emotions. </p> <p>Profoundly relaxing on a physical and mental level, it opens up the body on a whole new level.</p> <p><b>10h30-12h00 Yang Yoga </b></p> <p>In this Vinyasa Flow (breath synchronized movements), we flow like water, going smoothly from one pose to the other.  Soft warm ups prepare the body, energizing pranayama (breathing exercises) and invigorating sun salutations heat up, detox and stretch the body. Time is then taken to explore each pose individually, practicing mindfulness and awareness, ending in a brief relaxation at the end.</p> <p>Energizing and refreshing, this will wake up body and mind, oxygenate the blood, stretch and tone the body and relieve stress and tension</p> ','','',NULL),(13,2,NULL,'','2017-03-12 10:30:00','2017-03-12 13:00:00','','https://www.meetup.com/Luxembourg-Ultimate-Frisbee/events/237860441/','<p>Come out for Sunday practices with the Luxembourg Ultimate frisbee team. Practices are informal (though we do drills and play games), and beginners are welcome! Even if only a few sign up through Meetup, practices still take place ! Send Thierry a mail through Meetup or Check our website for contact details ! More information here:  <a href=\"http://www.ultimate-delux.org/Main_Page#Practice\"><a href=\"http://www.ultimatedelux.org/\" class=\"linkified\">http://www.ultimatedelux.org/</a></a></p> ','','',NULL),(14,2,NULL,'','2017-03-12 10:30:00','2017-03-12 12:00:00','','https://www.meetup.com/Yoga-in-Luxembourg/events/237860443/','<p>Join us on the mat for a beautiful session of Kundalini Yoga. Also called the Yoga of Awareness, can be enjoyed by everyone, no matter his or her age or physical ability.</p> <p>During this 90 minute class with a combination of asanas (postures), breathing techniques and meditation all the body is transformed into a new one: muscles, joints, organs and glands. We let all the toxins go as well as the information of the past that was stocked in our body. We feel fresh and healthy as we are building new organs and also a new body.</p> <p>Past habits leave while new ones are growing. So through the workout of our physical body we work also our organic, energetic and spiritual body.</p> <p>Book at www.claremariepilates.com</p> ','','',NULL),(15,2,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,'','https://www.meetup.com/Luxembourg-expats-and-repats/events/238250477/','','','',NULL),(16,2,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,'','https://www.meetup.com/Luxembourg-Soccer-Football-Meetup/events/238208562/','<p>Regular Sunday game. Please wear either a black or white shirt so we can split the team. Fun, casual game!</p> ','','',NULL),(17,2,NULL,'','2017-03-12 13:30:00','2017-03-12 17:30:00','','https://www.meetup.com/Luxembourg-Second-Hand-Creators-Markets-Meetup/events/237815478/','<p>2nd HAND SALE<br/>Lots of items for children, adults, families, singles and more!</p> <p>- WHEN: 12th March 2017<br/>- WHERE: B.U.R.O.S. Strassen<br/>- WHO: WeOrganize.lu is organizing a 2nd hand market.</p> <p>CUSTOMERS: Free Entrance<br/>VENDORS: To book a stand please contact [masked]. Places are limited</p> <p><img src=\"http://photos4.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/a/3/c/2/600_458441922.jpeg\" /></p> <p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1921125578123592/\" class=\"linkified\">https://www.facebook.com/events/1921125578123592/</a></p> ','','',NULL),(18,2,NULL,'','2017-03-13 17:00:00','2017-03-13 19:30:00','','https://www.meetup.com/Docker-Luxembourg/events/237696774/','<p>Docker Birthday #4 Celebration</p> <p><img src=\"http://photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/1/0/e/1/600_458344321.jpeg\" /></p> <p>\n\n\n\nJoin us in celebrating the Docker Project’s 4th birthday!</p> <p><br/>To celebrate together and warmly welcome newcomers into our community, we will provide Docker labs and courses to learn about Docker in a fun and inviting way.</p