 and Beginners are welcome ! We stretch and warm up, do drills, work strategy and play games. Even if only a few sign up through Meetup, practices still take place ! Send Thierry a mail through Meetup or Check our website for contact details ! More information here:  <a href=\"http://www.ultimate-delux.org/Main_Page#Practice\"><a href=\"http://www.ultimatedelux.org/\" class=\"linkified\">http://www.ultimatedelux.org/</a></a></p> ','','',NULL),(84,2,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,'','https://www.meetup.com/Zen-Mindfulness-in-Luxembourg/events/236315883/','<p>A 4 Week long Introduction to Meditation exploring the Zen Buddhist Tradition and the Western Mindfulness Teachings to see what they have to offer us to achieve a happier and more fulfilling life in the midst of the busy stressful world that we all share in.</p> <p>This course is relevant to everyone who breathes!</p> <p>The Syllabus:</p> <p>· “It is Good that You Are!”<br/>· “You are a Sensitive Human Being, not a Doing!”<br/>· “You are also the Dark Side!”<br/>· “Because the Wind loves to Caress the Leaves of the Trees”<br/>· “You are an Open Heart - Abide where there is no Abiding!”<br/>· “Love is all there is!”</p> <p>As well as meditation instruction and practice, and reflection-based group work, the classes will involve some experiential dance work, at times contact based, and some Qi Gong practices.</p> <p>Students will be expected to practice and carry out \'homework / home play\' and self-study of the topics throughout the course. This is not time demanding in a big way but does require some commitment on everyone\'s part to give value to this work.</p> <p>The fee for the course is 200 Eur which includes a booklet and access to guided meditations .</p> <p>Dates :</p> <p>Tuesday 4th  April[masked]<br/>Thursday 6th April[masked]<br/>Tuesday 18th  April[masked]<br/>Thursday 20th April[masked]<br/>Tuesday 25th  April[masked]<br/>Thursday 27th April[masked]</p> <p>One place is available on an unconditional dana basis - please contact me.</p> <p>To sign up, visit the teacher\'s website: <a href=\"http://www.easternpeace.co.uk/Zen-Mindfulness/Zen-Mindfulness-Classes.php\" class=\"linkified\">http://www.easternpeace.co.uk/Zen-Mindfulness/Zen-Mindfulness-Classes.php</a></p> ','','',NULL),(85,2,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,'','https://www.meetup.com/JSLuxembourg/events/238240237/','<p><b>We will serve Pizza and Beer, as usual!</b></p> <p>\n\n\nHere are the topics:</p> <p><b>Harder, Better, Faster, Stronger - A story about high-speed Javascript</b> - How to get maximum performance in real-time NodeJS applications running on embedded systems.<br/><i>by Florian Simon</i></p> <p>\n\n\n<b>Artificial web design</b> -  Are robots better designers than humans?<br/><i>by Patrick Beer</i></p> ','','',NULL),(86,2,NULL,'','2017-04-04 19:30:00','2017-04-04 21:15:00','','https://www.meetup.com/clubfotolu/events/230126083/','','','',NULL),(87,2,NULL,'','2017-04-05 17:30:00','2017-04-05 19:30:00','','https://www.meetup.com/Office-365-Meetup-Sudwest/events/237523538/','<p>Wir planen ein erstes Treffen der Usergroup in Saarbrücken bei der Data One GmbH.</p> <p>Agenda:</p> <p>- <b>Schnelle Kommunikation und Collaboration mit Microsoft Teams</b> (Andreas Knauer, Data One GmbH)</p> <p>- <b>Hybrid Identity - gespaltene Persönlichkeit oder Segen für den Anwender? </b>(Thomas Janetscheck, Data One GmbH)</p> <p>Im Anschluss an die Vorträge sind alle Teilnehmer zur lockeren Diskussion über Office 365 eingeladen.</p> ','','',NULL),(88,2,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,'','https://www.meetup.com/Luxembourg-expats-and-repats/events/236893741/','','','',NULL),(89,2,NULL,'','2017-04-06 12:00:00','2017-04-06 13:45:00','','https://www.meetup.com/Startup-Grind-Luxembourg/events/237931434/','<p><b><a href=\"http://www.startupgrind.com/events/details/startup-grind-luxembourg-presents-david-zimmer-inexio\"> THIS IS A PAID EVENT - PURCHASE YOUR TICKET HERE </a></b></p> <p><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/startup-grind/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,g_center,h_150,q_auto:good,w_150/v1/softlayer0/80135C1/media/v1/AUTH_d0619b05-07fc-49f0-8249-da585ea45ce5/events/luxembourg_luxembourg.jpg\" /></p> <p><b>David ZIMMER [Inexio]</b></p> <p>Startup Grind is the largest independent startup community, actively educating, inspiring, and connecting 1,000,000 entrepreneurs in over 200 cities. We nurture startup ecosystems in 85 countries through events, media, and partnerships with organizations like Google for Entrepreneurs. The cornerstone of our global community are monthly events featuring successful local founders, innovators, educators and investors who share lessons learned on the road to building great companies. Founded in Silicon Valley, Startup Grind has now hosted 5,000 fireside chats since its founding in 2010. To date, Startup Grind has helped millions of entrepreneurs find mentorship, connect to partners and hires, pursue funding, and reach new users</p> <p>\n\n\nOur Values</p> <p>We believe in making friends, not contacts.</p> <p>We believe in giving, not taking.</p> <p>We believe in helping others before helping yourself.</p> <p><b>Agenda</b></p> <p><b>12:00 pm</b> Networking and Food</p> <p><b>12:30 pm</b> Fireside Chat</p> <p><b>1:15 pm</b> Networking</p> <p><b>1:45 pm</b> End</p> <p><b>Speaker</b></p> <p><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/startup-grind/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,g_center,h_150,q_auto:good,w_150/v1/softlayer0/80135C1/media/v1/AUTH_d0619b05-07fc-49f0-8249-da585ea45ce5/events/David%20Zimmer%20Portrait%202016%20mittlere%20Gro%CC%88%C3%9Fe_G9BUIkQ.jpg\" /> David ZIMMER - Inexio</p> <p>Hosted By</p> <p><b>Steve Glange</b>, Luxembourg Director</p> <p><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/startup-grind/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,g_center,h_700,q_auto:good,w_700/v1/softlayer0/80135C1/media/v1/AUTH_d0619b05-07fc-49f0-8249-da585ea45ce5/avatars/steve_glange.jpg\" /></p> <p>Steve Glange launched the FirstTuesday network in the Greater Region and became board member of the global network. He is also a founding board member of Luxembourg Business Angels Network where he served as board member of EBAN. He was ambassador for XING in Luxembourg. He assisted launching and developing emerging companies and holds various advisory board seats. He is also a UN conference speaker and lecturer at Georgia Tech Institute. He uses his analytical and innovative skills around a good robusto cigar. Steve is an experienced networked solution broker.</p> <p><br/>Twitter: <a href=\"http://twitter.com/startupgrind_LU\">@startupgrind_LU</a> <b>Global Partner</b></p> <p><a href=\"http://www.google.com/entrepreneurs/\"> <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/startup-grind/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,g_center,h_100,q_auto:good/v1/softlayer0/80135C1/media/v1/AUTH_d0619b05-07fc-49f0-8249-da585ea45ce5/sponsors/google_for_entrepreneurs_-_final.png\" /> </a></p> <p>Google is committed to empowering entrepreneurs around the world through programs, partnerships, and our products.</p> <p><b>Partners</b></p> <p><a href=\"http://www.bpm.lu\"> <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/startup-grind/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,g_center,h_50,q_auto:good/v1/softlayer0/80135C1/media/v1/AUTH_d0619b05-07fc-49f0-8249-da585ea45ce5/sponsors/bpm.png\" /> </a></p> <p>Mobility and flexibility have become crucial in our lives.<br/>We provide mail forwarding and package forwarding to worldwide destinations, from 6 countries.<br/>In Luxembourg our customers pick up 24/7, at their BPM Mailbox or BPM PARCEL-STATION conveniently located in Luxembourg. BPM-Lux offers last mile and cross-border shopping solutions to cover private consumer and corporate needs, in Luxembourg, Europe, and Overseas.</p> <p><a href=\"http://www.cvf.lu\"> <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/startup-grind/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,g_center,h_50,q_auto:good/v1/softlayer0/80135C1/media/v1/AUTH_d0619b05-07fc-49f0-8249-da585ea45ce5/sponsors/cvf.png\" /> </a></p> <p>Le CVF, filmer par passion<br/>Le travail d\'équipe est la devise du seul club de cinéastes et vidéastes non-professionnel du Réiserbann, car avec un petit nombre de membres actifs, la coopération est un moyen efficace pour obtenir des résultats. Et que cette approche ait fait ses preuves, est démontrée par les nombreuses créations à succès national, mais aussi bien qu\'international.</p> <p><a href=\"http://luxfuturelab.lu\"> <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/startup-grind/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,g_center,h_50,q_auto:good/v1/softlayer0/80135C1/media/v1/AUTH_d0619b05-07fc-49f0-8249-da585ea45ce5/sponsors/lux-future-lab-logo_HtxP6HP.png\" /> </a></p> <p>We provide in the heart of Luxembourg City a physical space to support the development of skills and entrepreneurial projects in an interactive and dynamic environment. We want to encourage individuals at the crossroads of their professional development to improve their skills and to develop their entrepreneurial ideas.</p> <p><a href=\"http://www.mixvoip.com\"> <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/startup-grind/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,g_center,h_50,q_auto:good/v1/softlayer0/80135C1/media/v1/AUTH_d0619b05-07fc-49f0-8249-da585ea45ce5/sponsors/mixvoip_IQ9BCJF.png\" /> </a></p> <p>Your smart business telephony solution provider.<br/>Research &amp; Development - MIXvoip is a company that is based on new and innovative functionalities. MIXvoip continuously develops in-house cost-effective and customised solutions. MIXvoip properly adapts to the challenging requirements of the clients.<br/>Redundancy and security - MIXvoip focuses on security, stability and redundancy. Critical information, such as usernames and passwords, is always encrypted before being sent over the Internet.</p> <p><a href=\"http://www.siliconluxembourg.lu/\"> <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/startup-grind/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,g_center,h_50,q_auto:good/v1/softlayer0/80135C1/media/v1/AUTH_d0619b05-07fc-49f0-8249-da585ea45ce5/sponsors/xLOGO_SILICON-512x250.png\" /> </a></p> <p>the number one new media channel for